00:40:23,013 --> 00:40:25,004
- Get her out of those!
- Jamey?

476
00:40:25,093 --> 00:40:27,084
What's the number?

477
00:40:28,933 --> 00:40:34,053
- Hang in there. Come on. Come on, now.
